{"tid":1596040,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人/公司想用開CDN? 有折","createTime":"2019-09-26T10:38:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T06:41:30.000Z","uid":186797,"like":0,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4a19f8dc1904f9aaed1255741e9ba54a7b3fab09","tid":1596040,"uid":186797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T10:38:40.000Z","msg":"有冇人公司想用CDN服務? 唔想再用Cloudflare個類免費CDN服務<br />\n朋友做CDN公司, 我呢邊有折可以平D賣服務<br />\n有需要PM我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6c7aba0943ee8ef0ae6f9f368bb67e13a6a533","tid":1596040,"uid":148652,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:15:58.000Z","msg":"Cloudflare 又免費又好用，點解又哂錢搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28b0711818e45ef2ce7b971b64990ef4ef09fc2","tid":1596040,"uid":186797,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"quote":{"pid":"da6c7aba0943ee8ef0ae6f9f368bb67e13a6a533","tid":1596040,"uid":148652,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T03:15:58.000Z","msg":"Cloudflare 又免費又好用，點解又哂錢搵你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-28T06:41:30.000Z","msg":"關於免費：<br />\nCloudflare / Incapsula 等等提供免費版既CDN，好多功能你基本都用唔到，算係閹割版。咁當然功能上未有需要用到好Pro / 速度唔多需要保證既既可以忽略我，因為免費既可以Support到基本要求 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外我主要想問係比錢買Cloudflare / Incapsula等等企業版既用戶<br />\n如果你比錢用CDN，Cloudflare / Incapsula 等等比錢既版本會貴過好多家CDN<br />\n而另外如果係服務亞洲區，Cloudflare 速度一定唔會好過其他CDN<br />\n因為Cloudflare 分配線路係隨機，冇固定線路，而且係由美國出發。如果你地公司係好食速度既Product，比如即時遊戲或者係打入中國大陸市場等等，Cloudflare 唔算係一個好選擇<br />\n當然我只係提供一個選擇，大家可以按自己需求睇下要唔要<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6NLzyeT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6NLzyeT.png&h=d87c495c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1mewAte.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1mewAte.png&h=74f1afd4&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}